  <data name="OrdersAndDepositHeading" xml:space="preserve"><value>Accommodation booking and deposit</value></data>
  <data name="OrdersParagraph" xml:space="preserve"><value>Please send booking requests by e-mail and include your full name, accommodation dates, number of adults, and number and age of children if applicable. Your reservation will then be confirmed.</value></data>

  <data name="DepositHeading" xml:space="preserve"><value>Deposit</value></data>
  <data name="DepositParagraph" xml:space="preserve"><value>Please send a deposit of CZK 1,500 per person and stay by bank transfer after your reservation has been confirmed by e-mail. The reservation is cancelled if the deposit is not paid within 14 days of confirmation.</value></data>

  <data name="CancellationHeading" xml:space="preserve"><value>Cancellation fees</value></data>
  <data name="CancellationRow1Label" xml:space="preserve"><value>30 days or more before arrival</value></data>
  <data name="CancellationRow1Value" xml:space="preserve"><value>no fee</value></data>
  <data name="CancellationRow2Label" xml:space="preserve"><value>15–29 days before arrival</value></data>
  <data name="CancellationRow2Value" xml:space="preserve"><value>50% of the deposit</value></data>
  <data name="CancellationRow3Label" xml:space="preserve"><value>0–14 days before arrival</value></data>
  <data name="CancellationRow3Value" xml:space="preserve"><value>100% of the deposit</value></data>
  <data name="CancellationParagraph" xml:space="preserve"><value>If a replacement guest is provided for the cancelled booking and the original order is not changed, the deposit will be refunded in full. By confirming the reservation and/or paying for the stay, the client confirms that they have been informed of and accept these cancellation conditions. In case of early departure, the full booked stay will be charged.</value></data>

  <data name="PersonalDataHeading" xml:space="preserve"><value>Customer personal data</value></data>
  <data name="PersonalDataParagraph" xml:space="preserve"><value>By sending a booking request, the customer agrees to the storage of their personal data in the provider’s database. The provider undertakes to use this data solely for internal purposes related to the customer’s booking.</value></data>

